Package: firelens-monitor
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         python3 (>= 3.9),
         libxmlsec1-openssl
Description: Multi-vendor firewall monitoring solution
 FireLens Monitor collects real-time CPU, throughput, packet buffer,
 interface bandwidth, and session statistics from multiple firewalls
 simultaneously, storing them in a SQLite database with a web-based
 dashboard for visualization.
 .
 Supported vendors:
  - Palo Alto Networks (fully implemented)
  - Fortinet FortiGate (fully implemented)
  - Cisco Firepower (planned)
